3
00:01:51,679 --> 00:01:54,640
(Episode 29)
[K💖I💖S💖S💖K💖H]

4
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:04,119
Here, let me examine you.

5
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,319
Let me know if it hurts.

6
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,319
Doctor.

7
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,520
Is my condition not so good?

8
00:02:19,959 --> 00:02:21,039
You just had surgery.

9
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:22,559
It will take some time for it to recover.

10
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:29,639
I wonder when Ding Xiao Ying can see things.

11
00:02:30,199 --> 00:02:31,199
Don't worry.

12
00:02:31,479 --> 00:02:34,039
My colleague will help her look for a cornea donor.

13
00:02:34,519 --> 00:02:36,199
The police have also cleared you of suspicion.

14
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:39,319
I hope both of you can be discharged together.

15
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:40,840
Thank you.

16
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,079
Hui Zhen.

17
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,639
My dad woke up early this morning...

18
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:51,199
and made so much food.

19
00:02:51,199 --> 00:02:52,319
It's all your favorite dishes.

20
00:02:54,319 --> 00:02:55,799
But now that I'm discharged from the hospital,

21
00:02:56,079 --> 00:02:58,319
your dad will rush us to have a baby again.

22
00:02:59,919 --> 00:03:00,919
Hui Zhen.

23
00:03:01,319 --> 00:03:03,000
You can't blame my dad.

24
00:03:03,319 --> 00:03:04,319
Look.

25
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:06,440
We're almost 40 years old.

26
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:07,799
We don't even have a child.

27
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:11,120
It's normal for an old man like him to be worried.

28
00:03:11,639 --> 00:03:13,440
- I'm not blaming him. I just... - Le Le!

29
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,079
Le Le!

30
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,359
Le Le, slow down!

31
00:03:19,919 --> 00:03:21,319
- Are you okay? - I'm fine.

32
00:03:21,319 --> 00:03:22,359
Okay.

33
00:03:23,639 --> 00:03:24,680
Are you all right, Le Le?

34
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:27,319
- Are you all right? - I'm fine.

35
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:29,160
Let's go.

36
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:31,960
Hui Zhen.

37
00:03:32,079 --> 00:03:33,160
Hui Zhen.

38
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:34,600
What...

39
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:35,880
Hui Zhen.

40
00:03:37,519 --> 00:03:38,960
The taxi driver is back.

41
00:03:39,239 --> 00:03:40,519
As soon as she walked out of the hospital,

42
00:03:40,519 --> 00:03:42,519
she was hit by a child and fainted.

43
00:03:43,799 --> 00:03:45,160
By a child?

44
00:03:46,359 --> 00:03:47,400
Ne Zha.

45
00:03:48,479 --> 00:03:50,239
We did an electrocardiogram...

46
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:52,600
and there's no arrhythmia,

47
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,639
so our previous diagnosis was wrong.

48
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:56,039
It wasn't because of smart drugs.

49
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:03,199
Now that I think about it,

50
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:05,079
it should be...

51
00:04:05,079 --> 00:04:06,600
a cerebral embolism caused by a blood clot...

52
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,799
in the patient's blood.

53
00:04:08,519 --> 00:04:10,680
We did an arteriovenous ultrasound on her,

54
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:11,840
but there was nothing abnormal.

55
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:16,799
So we don't know why there's a clot in her blood.

56
00:04:17,199 --> 00:04:18,680
Could it be a lack of protein C?

57
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,880
It doesn't match symptoms of abnormal seizures.

58
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:22,799
I remember now.

59
00:04:23,919 --> 00:04:25,639
I heard about it from the patient's family.

60
00:04:25,639 --> 00:04:26,680
A few months ago,

61
00:04:26,799 --> 00:04:28,880
the patient has taken clomiphene continuously.

62
00:04:29,039 --> 00:04:30,400
To induce ovulation to get pregnant.

63
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:31,440
That's right.

64
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:33,079
Later, she felt uncomfortable and stopped.

65
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:35,319
Overdose of clomiphene...

66
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:37,720
does increase the risk of endometrial cancer.

67
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:40,720
Endometrial cancer can cause blood clots...

68
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,799
and that leads to a stroke.

69
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,840
I'll arrange a transvaginal ultrasound for her.

70
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:51,840
No thickening of the uterine lining.

71
00:04:51,999 --> 00:04:53,280
I don't see any lumps either.

72
00:04:53,559 --> 00:04:54,770
Does that mean she's fine?

73
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:57,650
Judging from the ultrasound, I don't see any signs of cancer.

74
00:05:01,039 --> 00:05:02,080
I told you.

75
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:03,840
We can't be that unlucky.

76
00:05:05,210 --> 00:05:06,239
Doctor.

77
00:05:07,039 --> 00:05:08,879
What happened to me?

78
00:05:08,879 --> 00:05:09,919
How about this?

79
00:05:09,999 --> 00:05:11,439
Let's consult the gynecologist later...

80
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:13,720
and let them do an endometrial biopsy.

81
00:05:14,039 --> 00:05:15,439
No abnormalities were found in the ultrasound.

82
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:16,600
Was it really necessary?

83
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,600
Is this your first day as a doctor?

84
00:05:17,770 --> 00:05:18,999
Don't you know the sensitivity of ultrasound...

85
00:05:18,999 --> 00:05:19,999
to tiny cancerous tissues?

86
00:05:20,119 --> 00:05:21,479
- What I mean is... - Doctor.

87
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:22,840
We'll do it.

88
00:05:24,439 --> 00:05:25,479
It's for peace of mind.

89
00:05:25,799 --> 00:05:27,770
Scraping the lining of the uterus is very harmful to the body.

90
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:29,160
You must be mentally prepared.

91
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:31,720
Will it hurt a lot?

92
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:32,770
It won't hurt.

93
00:05:32,770 --> 00:05:33,840
We'll use anesthesia.

94
00:05:33,919 --> 00:05:34,999
You'll be fine.

95
00:05:35,239 --> 00:05:36,650
I'm here.

96
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:40,239
Doctor.

97
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,999
We'll do it.

98
00:05:46,919 --> 00:05:47,919
Dr. Xiao.

99
00:05:48,359 --> 00:05:51,039
If my wife really has cancer,

100
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,799
how much longer can she live?

101
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:55,559
Don't worry.

102
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:57,039
There's a high chance of recovery...

103
00:05:57,039 --> 00:05:58,400
in the early stage of endometrial cancer.

104
00:05:58,559 --> 00:06:00,039
What's more, it's only suspicion.

105
00:06:00,559 --> 00:06:01,640
We have to wait for the scraping results...

106
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:02,840
for more details.

107
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:04,160
Maybe that's not the case.

108
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,720
You're Ma Hui Zhen's guardian, right?

109
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:11,280
Yes, I'm her husband.

110
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:15,720
When I first diagnosed the patient, I didn't see anything abnormal.

111
00:06:16,119 --> 00:06:18,559
But the ultrasound revealed that there was hypoechoic in the liver.

112
00:06:18,879 --> 00:06:20,119
There's fluid leaking from the abdominal cavity.

113
00:06:20,119 --> 00:06:21,879
What do you mean?

114
00:06:23,039 --> 00:06:25,400
Right now, there's a shadow in the liver.

115
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,160
There's fluid leaking from the abdominal cavity.

116
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:29,760
We have to quickly figure out what this shadow is.

117
00:06:30,359 --> 00:06:32,840
We will arrange an MRI of the abdomen for the patient.

118
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:38,080
I want to see her just once.

119
00:06:38,919 --> 00:06:40,160
Just once.

120
00:06:40,479 --> 00:06:42,039
You can't get out of bed yet.

121
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:50,039
Can't she see things at all?

122
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:54,359
She'll be able to see things when she finds the right cornea.

123
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:58,239
Is there anything you want to tell her?

124
00:06:58,359 --> 00:06:59,479
We can convey it to her.

125
00:07:03,439 --> 00:07:04,479
Forget it.

126
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:05,679
I won't bother her.

127
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:10,840
All right. You should get some rest.

128
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,320
Let's leave him alone.

129
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:22,600
I don't know if I should be touched or sad.

130
00:07:27,559 --> 00:07:30,119
He must be happy to sacrifice willingly...

131
00:07:30,559 --> 00:07:32,080
for the person he likes.

132
00:07:36,919 --> 00:07:37,919
Look.

133
00:07:38,879 --> 00:07:40,679
So the previous plan was wrong.

134
00:07:41,359 --> 00:07:42,999
The problem is not in the uterus.

135
00:07:43,200 --> 00:07:45,080
All the root causes are in the liver.

136
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:48,479
But I can't tell right now if it's benign or malignant.

137
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:49,799
Schedule for a biopsy.

138
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:52,679
But a liver tumor won't cause abnormal seizures.

139
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:54,439
There must be another reason.

140
00:07:56,239 --> 00:07:59,080
A normal liver tumor doesn't cause abnormal seizures,

141
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:01,439
but she was on smart drugs and clomiphene.

142
00:08:01,439 --> 00:08:03,280
Maybe when these two drugs are mixed together,

143
00:08:03,280 --> 00:08:04,919
it'll have some side effects that we don't know about.

144
00:08:05,559 --> 00:08:06,559
Maybe.

145
00:08:06,879 --> 00:08:08,879
Doctors can't use that to diagnose.

146
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:11,520
Should we just let it be then?

147
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:12,679
How can that be?

148
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:15,119
All necessary treatments and examinations have to be done.

149
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,559
What if the tumor gets worse?

150
00:08:17,439 --> 00:08:18,520
That's right.

151
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:21,359
Both of you can just proceed with the standard procedure.

152
00:08:21,799 --> 00:08:23,799
Leave the difficult puzzle-solving work to me.

153
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:30,879
All right.

154
00:08:30,919 --> 00:08:33,039
Let's see if you can solve it.

155
00:08:33,760 --> 00:08:34,760
Just wait and see.

156
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,799
There's a tumor in her liver?

157
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:39,160
Is it benign or malignant?

158
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:41,239
We'll need to do more tests to find out.

159
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:45,160
A normal liver tumor doesn't cause abnormal seizures,

160
00:08:45,479 --> 00:08:48,320
so Dr. Bai thinks that the patient may have other illnesses.

161
00:08:48,559 --> 00:08:50,400
He did it to show off.

162
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:52,720
Dr. Bai is so capable.

163
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:55,320
He can only fool ignorant nurses like you.

164
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:58,080
I think the patient's current situation...

165
00:08:58,519 --> 00:09:00,440
may have something to do with her pregnancy.

166
00:09:00,999 --> 00:09:02,200
What does it have to do with pregnancy?

167
00:09:02,639 --> 00:09:04,930
Didn't she take clomiphene for pregnancy?

168
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:06,960
Who knows if she has taken any other medications?

169
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,600
Nowadays, those fertility pills...

170
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:10,239
and birth control pills are all hormones.

171
00:09:10,239 --> 00:09:11,399
If you overdose, you'll have a problem.

172
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:13,519
One shouldn't take estrogen as she likes.

173
00:09:21,690 --> 00:09:22,759
What's wrong?

174
00:09:22,759 --> 00:09:23,810
What are you thinking about?

175
00:09:24,399 --> 00:09:25,399
Nothing.

176
00:09:25,519 --> 00:09:26,560
Let's eat.

177
00:09:32,239 --> 00:09:33,279
Dr. Xiao.

178
00:09:33,479 --> 00:09:34,999
I have something to tell you.

179
00:09:35,930 --> 00:09:38,239
Never mind. I'm not sure if I should tell you.

180
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:40,119
Tell me when you're ready.

181
00:09:40,119 --> 00:09:41,200
I'll just tell you.

182
00:09:42,399 --> 00:09:44,479
Regarding the patient who had abnormal seizures,

183
00:09:45,050 --> 00:09:46,359
she has been taking birth control pills.

184
00:09:46,519 --> 00:09:47,560
Birth control pills?

185
00:09:48,359 --> 00:09:50,119
Shouldn't she be taking fertility pills?

186
00:09:50,119 --> 00:09:51,119
Fertility pills?

187
00:09:51,239 --> 00:09:53,519
Her husband and father-in-law forced her to take it.

188
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,999
She didn't want to have a baby,

189
00:09:55,159 --> 00:09:57,399
so she secretly took birth control pills.

190
00:09:58,159 --> 00:10:01,479
I wonder if her abnormal seizures have something to do with this.

191
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:03,479
What kind of birth control pills was she on?

192
00:10:03,690 --> 00:10:04,960
This patient didn't say.

193
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,600
She just said they were birth control pills.

194
00:10:07,930 --> 00:10:10,560
Some of them do cause seizures.

195
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,080
Let's ask her about it.

196
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:13,479
Come on.

197
00:10:16,119 --> 00:10:17,600
If it's because of your past...

198
00:10:17,759 --> 00:10:19,519
that you don't want to get pregnant and don't want your family to know,

199
00:10:20,159 --> 00:10:21,519
we understand that.

200
00:10:21,999 --> 00:10:23,600
But for the sake of your health,

201
00:10:23,999 --> 00:10:25,050
I need you to tell me...

202
00:10:25,239 --> 00:10:27,159
which birth control pills you have taken.

203
00:10:30,399 --> 00:10:31,440
I'm sorry.

204
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,879
Dr. Tang is just worried about your condition.

205
00:10:34,879 --> 00:10:35,999
I've never taken birth control pills.

206
00:10:38,119 --> 00:10:40,359
Your husband just went to pay the bill.

207
00:10:40,879 --> 00:10:41,930
You can tell us.

208
00:10:41,930 --> 00:10:43,239
He won't be back so soon.

209
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,440
If you don't want your family to know,

210
00:10:48,690 --> 00:10:49,759
we can keep it a secret.

211
00:10:50,119 --> 00:10:51,119
That's your right.

212
00:10:52,119 --> 00:10:54,159
But right now, we need the information...

213
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:55,600
to diagnose your condition.

214
00:10:55,930 --> 00:10:57,479
Yes, think about it.

215
00:10:57,560 --> 00:10:59,759
You have a lump in your liver.

216
00:10:59,999 --> 00:11:01,519
It could be a malignant tumor.

217
00:11:01,519 --> 00:11:02,720
Don't try to scare me.

218
00:11:03,519 --> 00:11:06,159
Taking birth control pills won't cause me to grow a tumor.

219
00:11:07,759 --> 00:11:09,479
We're not trying to scare you.

220
00:11:09,879 --> 00:11:11,119
Previous cases have shown...

221
00:11:11,119 --> 00:11:12,560
that long-term use of certain types of contraceptives...

222
00:11:12,560 --> 00:11:14,840
is likely to cause hepatocellular adenoma.

223
00:11:15,279 --> 00:11:17,279
It also affects the dopamine system in the human body...

224
00:11:17,519 --> 00:11:18,519
and cause abnormal seizures.

225
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:20,800
What you said is possible,

226
00:11:21,239 --> 00:11:22,320
but you're not certain...

227
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,639
if it was caused by birth control pills.

228
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:24,960
It doesn't matter...

229
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:26,720
if the tumor is related to birth control pills or not...

230
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:28,879
or whether it's benign or malignant,

231
00:11:29,279 --> 00:11:32,560
but we may need to remove part of your liver tissue.

232
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,359
You don't want to remove...

233
00:11:36,359 --> 00:11:37,879
part of your liver tissue for nothing, right?

234
00:11:40,519 --> 00:11:42,080
If my husband and my father-in-law...

235
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:44,279
know about me taking birth control pills,

236
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:47,279
I'll never be able to have a peaceful life.

237
00:11:47,279 --> 00:11:48,840
Trust me this time.

238
00:11:49,159 --> 00:11:51,200
Your secret is safe with us.

239
00:11:58,440 --> 00:11:59,440
I've only taken...

240
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:01,639
