I'm sure you'll tell me one day.

734
00:41:25,440 --> 00:41:27,960
I'm a cardiac surgeon at Tangshan Hospital after all.

735
00:41:28,639 --> 00:41:30,929
I don't believe I can't open your heart.

736
00:41:31,889 --> 00:41:32,929
I...

737
00:41:33,839 --> 00:41:35,480
I just recovered.

738
00:41:36,960 --> 00:41:38,319
I'm going home to rest.

739
00:41:38,600 --> 00:41:39,600
I'll get going.

740
00:41:52,319 --> 00:41:53,409
Catherine.

741
00:41:53,600 --> 00:41:55,239
If I go back to Switzerland,

742
00:41:55,839 --> 00:41:57,600
can I still work at the hospital?

743
00:41:57,960 --> 00:41:59,759
Shirley, is that true?

744
00:41:59,929 --> 00:42:00,960
Yes.

745
00:42:01,119 --> 00:42:02,719
That's really great news.

746
00:42:03,369 --> 00:42:05,080
We were all so sad when you quit.

747
00:42:06,960 --> 00:42:08,889
I'll talk to the hospital tomorrow.

748
00:42:09,319 --> 00:42:10,440
Wait for my message.

749
00:42:10,719 --> 00:42:11,719
Thank you, Catherine.

750
00:42:24,279 --> 00:42:25,759
Okay, your temperature is 36.8.

751
00:42:25,759 --> 00:42:26,759
It's normal.

752
00:42:27,199 --> 00:42:28,279
Your blood pressure is good too.

753
00:42:29,600 --> 00:42:31,199
Thank you, Dr. Jiang.

754
00:42:31,759 --> 00:42:33,159
I'm Ms. Jiang, a nurse.

755
00:42:34,080 --> 00:42:35,279
It's the same thing.

756
00:42:35,279 --> 00:42:36,520
Both doctors and nurses save lives.

757
00:42:37,279 --> 00:42:38,369
What's wrong with her?

758
00:42:38,889 --> 00:42:39,960
Dr. Bai,

759
00:42:40,239 --> 00:42:41,889
Mrs. Zhang has chronic heart failure.

760
00:42:41,889 --> 00:42:43,639
She's here for a furosemide injection.

761
00:42:45,600 --> 00:42:47,080
Dr. Jiang is very attentive.

762
00:42:48,119 --> 00:42:49,440
Ma'am. Do you have a weak heart?

763
00:42:49,929 --> 00:42:52,279
It's chronic heart failure.

764
00:42:52,719 --> 00:42:53,839
Let me listen to your heart sounds.

765
00:42:54,119 --> 00:42:55,600
Let Dr. Bai examine you.

766
00:42:56,080 --> 00:42:57,119
- Come on. - Okay.

767
00:42:57,239 --> 00:42:58,319
Slowly.

768
00:43:04,929 --> 00:43:06,409
Dr. Xiao. You're back.

769
00:43:06,889 --> 00:43:07,889
How are you doing?

770
00:43:08,319 --> 00:43:09,319
I'm fine now.
